i fixed it just this code.

local.properties

    org.gradle.jvmargs=-XX\:MaxHeapSize\=512m -Xmx512m

and you should do this add this on app level build.gradle

    defaultConfig {
        applicationId &quot;yourProjectPackage&quot;
        minSdkVersion 16
        versionCode 1
        versionName &quot;1.0&quot;
        targetSdkVersion 28
    
        multiDexEnabled true //important
    }

